1
00:00:02,250 --> 00:00:03,624
[Previously]
This is the Blood of the Living Immortal.

2
00:00:03,875 --> 00:00:05,957
It will help you enter the Severing Self realm.

3
00:00:06,250 --> 00:00:09,041
Use the immortal blood to refine this strand of light
into your finger.

4
00:00:09,292 --> 00:00:11,499
Go beyond the pass and temper yourself first,
then enter the Severing Self realm.

5
00:00:11,833 --> 00:00:14,249
Call out all the top-ranked young kings.

6
00:00:15,208 --> 00:00:16,208
It’s not just Huang.

7
00:00:16,292 --> 00:00:17,666
Another vicious god has arrived.

8
00:00:18,042 --> 00:00:19,374
Today, right here,

9
00:00:19,708 --> 00:00:21,999
I will slaughter half of the young kings.

10
00:00:40,750 --> 00:00:42,041
The will of heaven manifests.

11
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:45,874
An origin ancient artifact and a sacred relic
of the same source are about to appear.

12
00:00:46,792 --> 00:00:49,624
Whoever obtains it can shatter the heavenly abyss
and open the path to emperorship.

13
00:00:53,667 --> 00:00:55,624
We vow to seize the sacred relic.

14
00:00:55,792 --> 00:00:56,999
And break the Emperor Pass.

15
00:00:57,792 --> 00:01:00,791
To fulfill our ancient ancestors’ long-cherished wish.

16
00:01:50,167 --> 00:01:51,374
Mere child’s play.

17
00:01:52,125 --> 00:01:54,332
How could it rival my Immortal Heaven Blade Art?

18
00:02:21,792 --> 00:02:22,792
It’s you.

19
00:02:23,208 --> 00:02:24,208
Too late.

20
00:02:25,208 --> 00:02:26,499
Martial Heaven King, hold on!

21
00:02:26,583 --> 00:02:27,999
We’re here to help you!

22
00:02:40,042 --> 00:02:41,042
Brother Wu.

23
00:02:41,542 --> 00:02:43,249
He’s clearly just a nameless nobody,

24
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,416
yet he managed to seal Brother Wu’s primordial spirit.

25
00:03:00,500 --> 00:03:02,999
Huang, I have bitterly cultivated for three years

26
00:03:03,500 --> 00:03:04,916
and comprehended the true meaning of immortality.

27
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:07,416
This chain shall sever evil spirits

28
00:03:07,625 --> 00:03:09,249
and sever my past shame as well.

29
00:03:09,542 --> 00:03:12,082
Turn to dust!

30
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:44,374
Now it’s your turn.

31
00:03:49,542 --> 00:03:50,542
Come at me together.

32
00:03:50,708 --> 00:03:52,041
This guy won’t last much longer.

33
00:03:52,542 --> 00:03:54,124
Even Huang is too afraid to show himself.

34
00:03:54,625 --> 00:03:56,124
This realm is already at its last gasp.

35
00:04:01,292 --> 00:04:03,249
I’ll trouble you two seniors to keep count for me.

36
00:04:48,625 --> 00:04:49,249
Ah!

37
00:04:49,625 --> 00:04:53,291
He’s already slain four of the top ten kings.

38
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,416
Counting that lion,

39
00:04:56,625 --> 00:04:57,625
that makes five.

40
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:02,374
Someone has slain five kings in a row.

41
00:05:03,208 --> 00:05:04,874
All Dragon Slayers, hear my command!

42
00:05:05,125 --> 00:05:06,624
Surround and kill this beast!

43
00:05:08,333 --> 00:05:09,249
The foreign army has arrived.

44
00:05:09,333 --> 00:05:10,082
All of you, retreat.

45
00:05:10,250 --> 00:05:11,250
Don’t linger here.

46
00:05:11,625 --> 00:05:12,625
What about you?

47
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,999
I’m naturally going to slaughter to my heart’s content.

48
00:05:15,023 --> 00:05:42,023
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

49
00:05:42,625 --> 00:05:44,249
Five great prodigies have fallen in a single day.

50
00:05:44,417 --> 00:05:45,417
The army’s morale is already shaken.

51
00:05:45,708 --> 00:05:46,708
Could the heavens truly be changing?

52
00:05:47,125 --> 00:05:48,332
But it was Huang who made a move.

53
00:05:48,625 --> 00:05:49,041
No.

54
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:51,124
It was a human youth we’ve never seen before.

55
00:05:51,458 --> 00:05:52,458
Besides Huang,

56
00:05:52,625 --> 00:05:54,041
there’s actually such a genius.

57
00:05:54,583 --> 00:05:56,582
Could it be that beings from another realm
are meddling again?

58
00:05:57,292 --> 00:05:59,291
This humiliation is even greater than the defeat at Great Scarlet Heaven.

59
00:05:59,750 --> 00:06:02,124
How can we allow him to keep trampling our clansmen’s corpses
to establish his might?

60
00:06:05,375 --> 00:06:06,582
We humbly request the Imperial Clan prodigies to emerge.

61
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,207
Suppress and kill that human and Huang.

62
00:06:08,375 --> 00:06:09,207
Restore our army’s prestige!

63
00:06:11,042 --> 00:06:12,042
The Imperial Clan…

64
00:06:12,625 --> 00:06:15,916
is not someone you can simply summon at will.

65
00:06:16,833 --> 00:06:19,207
Then may I ask if Brother He Ziming,
who ranks first, is willing to act?

66
00:06:19,583 --> 00:06:21,416
Ziming is at a critical moment in his breakthrough.

67
00:06:21,667 --> 00:06:22,957
Who would dare disturb him?

68
00:06:23,250 --> 00:06:26,582
The consequence would be death of both body and Dao.

69
00:06:28,708 --> 00:06:29,749
No need to worry.

70
00:06:30,208 --> 00:06:32,332
Everything inside and outside the Emperor Pass
is within sight.

71
00:06:33,375 --> 00:06:35,207
The experts from the Five King Clans have already emerged.

72
00:06:35,583 --> 00:06:38,874
We will surely use this person’s head
as a blood sacrifice to our fallen heroes.

73
00:06:41,708 --> 00:06:44,666
Besides, with the grand array being slaughtered day and night,

74
00:06:45,583 --> 00:06:47,416
how much longer can the Nine Heavens hold?

75
00:06:48,500 --> 00:06:50,499
Once our realm’s reinforcements arrive in force,

76
00:06:51,833 --> 00:06:53,582
both Huang and this youth

77
00:06:54,292 --> 00:06:55,499
will be finished.

78
00:07:09,417 --> 00:07:11,957
Just who was it that slew the five great kings of the foreign realm?

79
00:07:12,958 --> 00:07:14,124
Truly remarkable.

80
00:07:14,958 --> 00:07:16,041
Do you even need to ask?

81
00:07:16,292 --> 00:07:17,292
It must have been Huang.

82
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,000
Not necessarily.

83
00:07:19,208 --> 00:07:20,957
I have mastered the Heavenly Ear Passage.

84
00:07:21,833 --> 00:07:22,957
I just heard them say

85
00:07:23,125 --> 00:07:25,541
that a cultivator from some mysterious ancient land
seems to have entered our Emperor Pass.

86
00:07:26,083 --> 00:07:27,332
Could it be a being from the Forbidden Zones?

87
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,750
Heh.

88
00:07:57,875 --> 00:07:59,124
No one around.

89
00:07:59,708 --> 00:08:01,124
I no longer need to keep up the disguise.

90
00:08:07,250 --> 00:08:08,250
I’ve been marked.

91
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,124
The attack isn’t strong,

92
00:08:10,333 --> 00:08:11,374
but I can’t shake it off.

93
00:08:12,083 --> 00:08:13,874
This person is likely a One Escape realm expert.

94
00:08:24,917 --> 00:08:26,749
To leave the Emperor Pass, one must pass through the array platform.

95
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,916
Everyone who does will carry this special immortal light.

96
00:08:29,458 --> 00:08:31,624
Could this person actually be from inside the Emperor Pass?

97
00:08:42,417 --> 00:08:44,916
The more pressure this sword embryo receives,
the greater its power becomes.

98
00:08:45,417 --> 00:08:46,832
I’ll use it to break through.

99
00:08:48,208 --> 00:08:49,208
Break!

100
00:08:59,417 --> 00:09:00,957
Not a bad sword.

101
00:09:01,458 --> 00:09:02,707
It’s mine now.

102
00:09:03,417 --> 00:09:04,417
Dream on.

103
00:09:33,167 --> 00:09:34,167
What rotten luck.

104
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:36,499
You actually alerted the Ironblood Ancient Tree.

105
00:09:40,917 --> 00:09:41,707
Moon…
No, wait.

106
00:09:41,875 --> 00:09:43,457
You didn’t stumble in here by accident.

107
00:09:44,042 --> 00:09:48,374
You took one look at the map and dared to risk your life
betting on the Ironblood Ancient Tree as your way out.

108
00:09:48,875 --> 00:09:50,416
You’ve got some nerve.

109
00:09:51,042 --> 00:09:52,166
Senior flatters me.

110
00:09:53,125 --> 00:09:54,582
Escorting this junior all the way here

111
00:09:54,708 --> 00:09:55,708
must have been exhausting.

112
00:09:55,833 --> 00:09:56,833
What’s wrong?

113
00:09:56,958 --> 00:09:58,374
Not planning to show your true face?

114
00:09:58,583 --> 00:10:00,374
So I can at least know who my benefactor is.

115
00:10:01,250 --> 00:10:02,624
Sharp tongue.

116
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,124
In that case,

117
00:10:13,333 --> 00:10:15,916
you can just stay inside and behave yourself.

118
00:10:16,208 --> 00:10:18,166
I’ll go call for help right now.

119
00:10:19,375 --> 00:10:21,916
I wonder which family is behind this little scheme this time.

120
00:10:22,542 --> 00:10:24,666
The location marked on the treasure map is nearby.

121
00:10:24,958 --> 00:10:25,958
I need to hurry.

122
00:10:26,333 --> 00:10:28,082
Before the foreign realm’s people arrive,

123
00:10:28,583 --> 00:10:30,666
I must find that mysterious supreme treasure they’re after.

124
00:10:56,708 --> 00:10:58,541
This mountain range is truly terrifying.

125
00:10:59,125 --> 00:11:01,124
Not only are there shape-shifting divine herbs everywhere,

126
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:04,666
even the flying birds are One Escape realm powerhouses.

127
00:11:05,125 --> 00:11:07,791
They could wipe out an entire divine mountain with one strike.

128
00:11:29,458 --> 00:11:32,374
This is the power of the Immortal Dao.

129
00:11:33,167 --> 00:11:35,041
Just what kind of monster is hidden in this place?

130
00:11:55,292 --> 00:11:57,332
A little calf formed from Yellow Dao Immortal Gold.

131
00:12:01,458 --> 00:12:02,916
Looks like it’s mine now.

132
00:12:03,125 --> 00:12:04,416
Be good and slow down.

133
00:12:09,458 --> 00:12:10,458
You…

134
00:12:11,125 --> 00:12:12,125
What?

135
00:12:28,458 --> 00:12:31,207
Wait—stop! Sit… sit down!

136
00:12:38,208 --> 00:12:40,874
Hey, I don’t know what’s going on,

137
00:12:41,250 --> 00:12:43,832
but today my heart suddenly feels so warm.

138
00:13:06,083 --> 00:13:07,124
Just a light bump

139
00:13:07,958 --> 00:13:09,749
and it inflicts origin Dao injury.

140
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:12,957
I’m afraid most people couldn’t bear this kind of “affection.”

141
00:13:21,583 --> 00:13:22,999
Inside the Emperor Pass,

142
00:13:23,333 --> 00:13:25,624
there are actually people who understand true righteousness.

143
00:13:25,917 --> 00:13:26,332
Willing to work with us to merge the two realms.

144
00:13:26,333 --> 00:13:28,416
Willing to work with us to merge the two realms.

145
00:13:28,667 --> 00:13:30,874
This is truly a blessing for our realm.

146
00:13:39,083 --> 00:13:40,457
You flatter me, my lord.

147
00:13:41,333 --> 00:13:42,707
I simply wish

148
00:13:43,208 --> 00:13:47,082
to fight for a slim chance of survival for the younger generation of my clan.

149
00:13:47,208 --> 00:13:49,249
The spiritual essence of this world

150
00:13:50,167 --> 00:13:51,167
is truly…

151
00:13:51,208 --> 00:13:52,832
captivating.

152
00:13:52,958 --> 00:13:55,499
The Great Dao resonates with me so perfectly.

153
00:13:58,792 --> 00:14:01,124
A natural land for achieving the Dao.

154
00:14:03,417 --> 00:14:04,582
Forgive my rudeness.

155
00:14:05,083 --> 00:14:07,041
So you are a fairy.

156
00:14:12,083 --> 00:14:15,832
This is the power of immortality.

157
00:14:16,250 --> 00:14:17,541
Fairy, your great righteousness

158
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:19,291
will be etched in our hearts.

159
00:14:19,667 --> 00:14:21,499
When our realm rules supreme one day

160
00:14:21,583 --> 00:14:22,957
and the two realms become one—

161
00:14:23,125 --> 00:14:26,332
we will certainly not mistreat you or your clansmen.

162
00:14:27,542 --> 00:14:30,041
This shall be my certificate of allegiance.

163
00:14:31,042 --> 00:14:32,332
I’ll take my leave first.

164
00:14:32,708 --> 00:14:34,624
In the future, should you have any orders,

165
00:14:34,958 --> 00:14:37,957
my Wind Clan will gladly go through fire and water for you.

166
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:44,291
Hahahaha!

167
00:14:44,958 --> 00:14:47,291
So it really is Huang.

168
00:14:47,625 --> 00:14:49,916
He’s trapped inside the Divine Herb Mountain Range.

169
00:14:50,167 --> 00:14:51,832
Heaven is helping me!

170
00:14:52,083 --> 00:14:54,041
What a magnificent gift.

171
00:14:54,125 --> 00:14:57,374
It fits perfectly with our realm’s grand plan.

172
00:14:57,667 --> 00:14:59,457
Hahahaha!

173
00:14:59,833 --> 00:15:00,916
Assemble!

174
00:15:01,125 --> 00:15:02,499
Right here.

175
00:15:02,833 --> 00:15:04,707
Surround and kill Huang!

176
00:15:05,625 --> 00:15:06,625
Understood!

177
00:15:08,667 --> 00:15:09,667
[Shrouding the Heavens – First Theatrical Film: ‘Battle Against the Heavens’ — See You on the Emperor’s Path, April 4, 2026]
The so-called Emperor Path

178
00:15:09,875 --> 00:15:10,875
is not one of invincibility.
[Shrouding the Heavens – First Theatrical Film: ‘Battle Against the Heavens’ — See You on the Emperor’s Path, April 4, 2026]

179
00:15:11,542 --> 00:15:12,542
Ye Fan…

180
00:15:13,042 --> 00:15:15,041
It’s truly a shame

181
00:15:15,208 --> 00:15:16,374
that we were born in the same era.

182
00:15:17,792 --> 00:15:18,792
If you want to fight, then fight.

183
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,082
Why make so many excuses?

184
00:15:21,836 --> 00:15:23,578
[Shrouding the Heavens – First Theatrical Film: ‘Battle Against the Heavens’]

185
00:15:23,907 --> 00:15:33,107
[Perfect World: The Crisis Arrives]

186
00:15:34,055 --> 00:15:37,945
[Phoenix Nirvana: After the Phoenix Nirvana, the old self is shed, the soul is reborn, and one is reborn from the flames. Afterward, the phoenix transforms, rising again with a stronger body and greater power. It is said that the phoenix, after nirvana, can evolve into an even more powerful being and reach a higher realm.]

187
00:15:37,969 --> 00:16:13,969
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

